{"id":34,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":34,"title":"Chapter 31: Captain Moroni Defeats Zerahemnah","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 31","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 31"],["h1","Captain Moroni Defeats Zerahemnah"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p3"},"Zerahemnah, the leader of the Lamanites, wanted his people to continue hating the Nephites and to make them their slaves."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.5,8"},"Alma 43:5, 8"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p5"},"The Nephites wanted to keep their land and their families free. They also wanted to be free to worship God."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.9"},"Alma 43:9"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p7"},"Captain Moroni was the leader of the Nephite armies. When the Lamanites came to fight, Moroni and his armies met them in the land of Jershon."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.15-16"},"Alma 43:15–16"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p9"},"Captain Moroni had prepared his army with weapons, shields, armor, and thick clothing."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.18-19"},"Alma 43:18–19"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p11"},"The Lamanites had a larger army but were scared when they saw the Nephites’ armor—the Lamanites were wearing very little clothing."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.20-21"},"Alma 43:20–21"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p13"},"The Lamanite army did not dare fight Captain Moroni’s army. The Lamanites ran into the wilderness and decided to attack a different Nephite city."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.22"},"Alma 43:22"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p15"},"Moroni sent spies to watch the Lamanites. He also asked Alma to pray to the Lord for help. The Lord told Alma where the Lamanites would attack."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.23-24"},"Alma 43:23–24"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p17"},"When Moroni received Alma’s message, he left some soldiers to guard Jershon and marched the rest of them to meet the Lamanites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.25"},"Alma 43:25"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p19"},"Captain Moroni’s soldiers hid on both sides of the river Sidon, waiting to trap the Lamanite army."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.27,31-35"},"Alma 43:27, 31–35"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p21"},"A battle began, and the Lamanites tried to escape by crossing the river, but more Nephites were waiting for them on the other side."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.36,39-41"},"Alma 43:36, 39–41"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p23"},"Fighting harder than they ever had before, Zerahemnah and his army killed many Nephites. The Nephites cried to the Lord for help."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.43-44,49"},"Alma 43:43–44, 49"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f12"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_12.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p25"},"The Lord strengthened the Nephite army. The army surrounded the Lamanites, and Moroni ordered the fighting to stop."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p26"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.50,52-54"},"Alma 43:50, 52–54"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f13"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_13.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p27","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p27"},"Moroni told Zerahemnah that the Nephites did not want to kill the Lamanites or make them their slaves."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p28"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.1-3"},"Alma 44:1–3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f14"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_14.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p29"},"Moroni said the Lamanites could not destroy the Nephites’ faith in Jesus Christ. He said God would continue to help the Nephites fight as long as they were faithful."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p30"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.4"},"Alma 44:4"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f15"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_15.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p31"},"Moroni ordered Zerahemnah to give up his weapons. The Lamanites would not be killed if they promised never to fight the Nephites again."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p32"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.5-6"},"Alma 44:5–6"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f16"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_16.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p33"},"Zerahemnah gave Moroni his weapons but would not promise not to fight. Moroni handed the weapons back so the Lamanites could defend themselves."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p34"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.8,10"},"Alma 44:8, 10"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f17"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_17.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p35"},"Zerahemnah rushed at Moroni to kill him, but a Nephite soldier hit and broke Zerahemnah’s sword."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p36"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.12"},"Alma 44:12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f18"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_18.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p37","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p37"},"Then the soldier cut off Zerahemnah’s scalp, put it on the tip of his sword, and raised it into the air."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p38","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p38"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.12-13"},"Alma 44:12–13"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f19"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_19.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p39","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p39"},"The Lamanites would fall as the scalp had fallen, he told them, unless they gave up their weapons and promised never to fight again."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p40","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p40"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.14"},"Alma 44:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f20"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_20.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p41","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p41"},"Many Lamanites placed their weapons at Moroni’s feet and promised not to fight. They were allowed to go free."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p42","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p42"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.15"},"Alma 44:15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f21"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_21.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p43","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p43"},"Furious, Zerahemnah stirred up the rest of his soldiers to fight. Moroni’s soldiers killed many of them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p44","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p44"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.16-18"},"Alma 44:16–18"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f22"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_22.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p45","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p45"},"When Zerahemnah saw that he and all his men would be killed, he begged Moroni to spare them. He promised never to fight the Nephites again."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p46","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p46"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.19"},"Alma 44:19"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.f23"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_034_23.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p47","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p47"},"Moroni stopped the fighting and took the Lamanites’ weapons. After they promised not to fight, the Lamanites left."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p48","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-31-captain-moroni-defeats-zerahemnah.p48"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.20,23"},"Alma 44:20, 23"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
